metadata_description: ProduKey is a small utility that displays the ProductID and the CD-Key of Microsoft Office (Microsoft Office 2003. Microsoft Office 2007). Windows (Including Windows 8/7/Vista). Exchange Server. and SQL Server installed on your computer. You can view this information for your current running operating system. or for another operating system/computer - by using command-line options. This utility can be useful if you lost the product key of your Windows/Office. and you want to reinstall it on your computer.
